title: Show Shares First Country Songs They Ever Heard + P!NK Calls In To Talk To Bobby About Her Song With Chris Stapleton
itunes:title: Show Shares First Country Songs They Ever Heard + P!NK Calls In To Talk To Bobby About Her Song With Chris Stapleton
description:
Bobby and the crew each share the first country song they ever heard. P!NK calls in to talk to Bobby about her new music and collaborating with Chris Stapleton. Also, the show recaps the iHeartCountry Festival.
